api
api is a python script that uses the python flask framework to create a simple API. It use the prometheus_client library to track metrics.

Installation 
Use the attached dockerfile to create a docker image and run the image.
The api file and the dockerfile need to be placed in same directory. 
Then build the docker image ;
docker build dockerfile
Use the image to create a container.
The api will be running on the container 
The API uses port 8080
